WEBVTT

00:00:00.151 --> 00:00:04.663
The world of work is undergoing a profound transformation driven by artificial intelligence.

00:00:05.425 --> 00:00:11.981
We are moving into the era of agentic AI, where AI systems act autonomously within multi-step workflows.

00:00:12.823 --> 00:00:15.430
Your mandate is no longer managing linear tasks.

00:00:16.071 --> 00:00:20.360
It is redesigning entire workflows to orchestrate human AI symbiosis.
